"text": "Details
Product Quick Look
This iPhone 13 Pro Max Case combines beauty and functionality to provide the best protection and fashion for your phone. Equipped with shock-absorbent TPU frame and tempered glass back, it perfectly shields the surface of your phone from damage and allows easy access to all features, functions and ports thanks to its exact cutouts and precise design. Why Choosing Us? - Advanced printing pattern design adds elegant and luxury taste.- Constructed of heavy duty 9H tempered glass back and soft TPU frame. - Offers full protection against scratch, dust, collision, abrasion, dropping and shocking.- Great camera protection and precise cut-out for all controls and features.- Easy to take on/off the case.Package: 1x Case for Apple iPhone 13 Pro MaxPlease Note: Accessory only, phone not includedCustomer Service: We provide every customer with 60 days money back warranty, free return and replacement. Every question will be responded within 24 hours, just feel free to send us an email.
Suitable model: Designed exclusively for iPhone 13 Pro Max with 6.7-inch.
Advanced Printing: Covered with tempered glass using the world's top printing technology. Make iPhone 13 Pro Max case pattern brighter, clearer and more vivid.
Top Glass: Hard tempered glass back sheet has excellent characteristics such as abrasion resistance, scratch resistance and impact resistance. Make your iPhone 13 Pro Max case have a high-end texture while also having strong protection.
Easy to Use: the Bumper is made of TPU material which is good for absorbing shock and protecting the iPhone 13 Pro Max. Precise hole positions allow you to smoothly press various phone buttons. It is easy to install and remove and won't scratch your phone.
Safe Design: Raised edges protect screen from scratches and facedown impacts. Reinforced rubber corners aborb impacts to reduce possibility of shatters.
Display size: 6.7 inches
Product Dimensions	6.3 x 3.15 x 0.39 inches
Item Weight	1.76 ounces
Special Features	Heavy Duty Protection
Other display features	Wireless
Form Factor	Bumper
Colour	Neon Turtle
Manufacturer	Anemone45
Date First Available	September 16, 2021
